# Tamagotchi Virtual Pet Game

A JavaFX-based virtual pet simulation game where you can care for and interact with digital pets.

## Features

- Three pet types: Dog, Cat, and Bunny
- Manage pet stats: Health, Happiness, Energy, Fullness
- In-game currency system (Dabloons)
- Save/Load game functionality
- Play time restrictions (parental controls)
- Fullscreen mode support

## Requirements

- Java JDK 23 or later
- JavaFX 23 or later
- Git (optional, for cloning)

## To run

- Run './run.sh' to compile and run
- If error Permission Declined run 'chmod +x run.sh'
